    "ragtruth_id": "127",
    "text": "April 8 was not only significant for \"Lost\" fans, but also for fans of the 1995 film \"Empire Records\" as it was \"Rex Manning Day.\" The film centers around an independent record store where former pop idol Rex Manning makes an appearance on April 8. Other notable dates from films include April 14, the date of the sinking of the Titanic in the movie \"Titanic,\" April 25, deemed the perfect date in \"Miss Congeniality,\" October 3, known as \"Mean Girls Day,\" and October 21, 2015, the date Marty McFly and his friends travel to in \"Back to the Future Part II.\"",
